  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to <i>Starry Trace</i>!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a relaxing yet thought-provoking puzzle game. With over 100 meticulously designed levels, the difficulty gradually increases, making it increasingly addictive as you play. Are you ready to embark on this starry painting journey?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose a star, leave your mark!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/913e5430ad583c3fd26fe7837f2b1607.poster.avif?t=1773750716\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/913e5430ad583c3fd26fe7837f2b1607.webm?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/913e5430ad583c3fd26fe7837f2b1607.mp4?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tap the star you want to move, but remember: you can only switch stars after clearing all from the grid.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fill the grid, complete the pattern!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/8c8b888a46096be3551da2dc8afdad4e.poster.avif?t=1773750716\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/8c8b888a46096be3551da2dc8afdad4e.webm?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/8c8b888a46096be3551da2dc8afdad4e.mp4?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Finish the target design within the allowed moves to win. Simple controls, but mastering it takes strategy!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More modes, endless challenges!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/aae55c7b8fef2f3c35ba9c3c2a1e9467.poster.avif?t=1773750716\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/aae55c7b8fef2f3c35ba9c3c2a1e9467.webm?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/aae55c7b8fef2f3c35ba9c3c2a1e9467.mp4?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/56b47df7850b1d6db45e4c65c60edb33.poster.avif?t=1773750716\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/56b47df7850b1d6db45e4c65c60edb33.webm?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3593600/extras/56b47df7850b1d6db45e4c65c60edb33.mp4?t=1773750716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random mode, shoot mode - each time it's a completely new challenge!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Limited Moves</strong>: Plan carefully to solve puzzles in minimal steps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progressive Unlocks</strong>: Beat a level to unlock the next—get ready for tougher challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint System</strong>: Stuck? Tap the lightbulb icon to view example solutions and help you progress smoothly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Mode</strong>: Enjoy fresh puzzles every time with infinite randomized stages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shoot Mode</strong>: Rotate the grid and shoot stars to paint, matching the target pattern  to clear the level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed Run</strong>: Stop the timer when you finish—race against the clock!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chill Soundtrack</strong>: Soothing BGM keeps you relaxed even during marathon sessions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Support for controllers</strong>: Connect a controller, kick back, and puzzle away with ease.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎉 Start Your Celestial Adventure Now! 🎉</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re sharpening your mind or unwinding, <i>Starry Trace</i> delivers endless fun. Who will become the ultimate \"Starry Artist\"?</p>",
