ons and help you progress smoothly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Mode</strong>: Enjoy fresh puzzles every time with infinite randomized stages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shoot Mode</strong>: Rotate the grid and shoot stars to paint, matching the target pattern  to clear the level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed Run</strong>: Stop the timer when you finish—race against the clock!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chill Soundtrack</strong>: Soothing BGM keeps you relaxed even during marathon sessions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Support for controllers</strong>: Connect a controller, kick back, and puzzle away with ease.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎉 Start Your Celestial Adventure Now! 🎉</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re sharpening your mind or unwinding, <i>Starry Trace</i> delivers endless fun. Who will become the ultimate \"Starry Artist\"?</p>",
